### Orchestration Module Updates

#### [MODIFY] [intent_agent.py](file:///D:/Evolve_Robot_Lab/Project/FilmDB_Demo/backend/app/intent_agent.py)
Add 4 new intents to the system prompt:
- `PLOT_EXPLANATION` — "explain the plot of X", "what is X about" (currently caught by ENTITY_LOOKUP/ANALYTICAL_EXPLANATION)
- `CRITIC_SUMMARY` — "what do critics say about X", "reviews of X" (currently REVIEWS)
- `MOVIE_SIMILARITY` — "movies similar to X" (currently RECOMMENDATION)
- `FILMOGRAPHY` — "filmography of X", "movies directed by X" (currently PERSON_LOOKUP)

Add classification examples for each.

