### KB Mapping Pipeline Update

#### [MODIFY] [kb_mapping.py](file:///D:/Evolve_Robot_Lab/Project/FilmDB_Demo/rag/kb_mapping.py)
Add a new Layer 1.5: `person_index.parquet`
- Source: [title.crew.tsv](file:///D:/Evolve_Robot_Lab/Project/FilmDB_Demo/kb/IMDb/title.crew.tsv/title.crew.tsv) + [title.principals.tsv](file:///D:/Evolve_Robot_Lab/Project/FilmDB_Demo/kb/IMDb/title.principals.tsv/title.principals.tsv) + [name.basics.tsv](file:///D:/Evolve_Robot_Lab/Project/FilmDB_Demo/kb/IMDb/name.basics.tsv/name.basics.tsv)
- Aggregates: for each `nconst`, collect `name`, `profession`, and list of [(imdb_id, category/role)](file:///D:/Evolve_Robot_Lab/Project/FilmDB_Demo/backend/app/conversation_engine.py#71-74)
- Filters: only keep people with ≥1 movie credit (from [movie_entity](file:///D:/Evolve_Robot_Lab/Project/FilmDB_Demo/rag/kb_mapping.py#85-176))
- Expected size: ~50-100 MB parquet

