### Manual Verification
- Start the backend (`uvicorn`) and use the chat UI
- Test queries like:
  - "Tell me about Inception" → should return KB data with rating, overview
  - "Explain the plot of The Shawshank Redemption" → should return Wikipedia plot
  - "What do critics say about The Dark Knight" → should return RT reviews summary
  - "Movies similar to Interstellar" → should return tag-based recommendations
  - "Top rated Action movies" → should return KB-filtered list
  - "Christopher Nolan filmography" → should return film list from person_index
  - "Compare Inception and Interstellar" → should return side-by-side data
